<section>
  <h2 id="nodemon">Nodemon</h2>

  <p>Use <strong>nodemon</strong> to automatically restart your server whenever file changes occur:</p>

  <pre><code data-trim="" contenteditable="">
# install it
npm install -g nodemon
</code></pre>

  <pre><code data-trim="" contenteditable="">
# run your project calling nodemon... and the executable for your project
nodemon bin/www
</code></pre>

  <pre><code data-trim="" contenteditable="">
# sometimes you have to specify the exact extensions to monitor
nodemon bin/www -e "js hbs css html"
</code></pre>

</section>

